      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1115 - Saʿd ibn Ismail narrated from his father, who narrated from al-Ridha (as), that He said:\n\"I asked him about a man who commits sins ; should one pray behind him or not?\"\nImam (as) said: \"No.\""
